data.description: This is a must see, Tons of potential most of the work has been done just needs to be finished. 3 bedroom , 2 bath, Carport with attached laundry room and storage room. almost completely remodeled ,   New Front Door, New French Doors , New Prehung bedroom Doors, Closet Doors, & door casings,  New Wood laminate flooring in Bedrooms and Living room , tile flooring , New Kitchen Cabinets, New Baseboards, New Appliances - Refrigerator, Microwave, Oven, Dish Washer, Washer/Dryer,  New Vanity, Shower and Toilet in guest Bathroom, New outlets. HUGE Lanai with Vinyl windows, Seller is leaving everything purchased to finish house including Master Bathroom Vanity with granite countertop and 2 vessel sinks, toilet , laminate flooring for lanai, kitchen cabinets,  light fixtures , sinks. Guest house in the rear needs total rehab. Extra storage shed. Fenced Yard. Seller is willing to help buyers by paying 3% towards buyers closing cost . Community boat ramp just down the street.
